glib-perl: glib-perl (GLib Bindings for Perl)
glib-perl:
glib-perl: glib-perl is a set of perl bindings for the Glib library. These 
glib-perl: modules make it easy to write GTK and GNOME applications using 
glib-perl: Perl. It includes the ExtUtils-Depends, ExtUtils-PkgConfig and Glib
glib-perl: bindings for perl.
